first- avatar doesn't overwrite vigor. And its not useless. Untill My guild pallys get BMB upgrade I now use SV on ALL fights exept AE dispell due to 90% of the right clickies are Grim aura and doesn't stack with SV.
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
Infusion of spirit - It isn't the stamina that is causing a problem. SoV doesn't even give stamina. It gives dex. The problem is IoS dex is in the same slot as SoV dex so it can't stack. FoS shares a Strength slot with IoS so it can't stack. FoS does NOT give agi. 
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
